You find yourself in the Courtyard. It seems a bit quiet here.
You enter the courtyard in Hagrid’s arms alongside Voldemort, Nagini and his followers. The students and Faculty come outside to see them as you hear Voldemort say, “Harry Potter is dead!”. As everyone stand back in disbelief, he continues and tells everyone to “Come forward and join us, or die”.  In the silence afterwards, many of the students from the Slytherin house join their parents; however, Neville Longbottom begins to speak out against Voldemort.
